NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Acme::CPANLists - Plugin to use when building
    Acme::CPANLists::* distribution

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.03 of
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Acme::CPANLists (from Perl distribution
    Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Acme-CPANLists), released on 2017-07-28.

SYNOPSIS
    In dist.ini:

     [Acme::CPANLists]

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin is to be used when building "Acme::CPANLists::*"
    distribution. It currently does the following:

    *   Fill the Abstract from the first module/author list's summary

    *   Add prereq to the mentioned modules (phase=x_mentions,
        relationship=x_mentions)

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Acme-CPANLists>.

